    "en": "Residence authorisation for highly qualified professionals",
    "zh-Hans": "高技能专业人士居留许可"
  },
  "aliases": [
    "Spain highly qualified professional permit",
    "UGE highly qualified professional route"
  ],
  "status": "active",
  "status_note_md": {
    "en": "The Spanish Ministry of Inclusion describes this as a temporary residence-and-work authorisation. The ministry page was last updated in May 2025 and notes that the rules in force when the application is filed control.",
    "zh-Hans": "西班牙包容、社会保障和移民部将其描述为临时居留和工作许可。该部页面最后更新于 2025 年 5 月，并说明申请提交时有效的规则才具有决定作用。"
  },
  "summary_md": {
    "en": "An employer-linked Spanish residence-and-work route for a foreign professional who will perform work requiring higher-education qualifications or, exceptionally, equivalent professional experience.",
    "zh-Hans": "面向与雇主相关联的西班牙居留和工作途径，适用于从事需要高等教育学历，或在特殊情况下需要相当专业经验的外国专业人士。"
  },
  "good_for_md": {
    "en": "Professionals with a Spanish employment arrangement and an employer able to support the mobility-international application and provide the required qualification or experience evidence.",
    "zh-Hans": "适合拥有西班牙雇佣安排，且雇主能够支持国际流动申请并提供所需学历或经验证明的专业人士。"
  },
  "not_good_for_md": {
    "en": "Applicants seeking self-sponsored remote work, a visitor route, or a path with a known salary threshold or direct PR outcome that is not established in the retained official pages.",
    "zh-Hans": "不适合寻求自我担保远程工作、访问者途径，或需要已知薪资门槛和直接永久居留结果但保留官方页面尚未确认这些内容的申请人。"
  },
